INSERT INTO `product` VALUES ('0003066d-6603-4cff-a4c6-1bb67fa51c27','100-100001351WOF','AMD RYZEN Threadripper 7970X 4.0Ghz 32-Core CPU','Let AMD Ryzenâ„˘ Threadripperâ„˘ processors be the productivity-boosting engine at the heart of your next professional workstation. When your business needs to get the job done, moving the deadline isnâ€™t an option. Artists, architects, and engineers require a highly expandable workstation platform to deliver unmatched reliable full-spectrum performance with enterprise-class security features, manageability, and unrivaled expandability.\nBuilt on the leading Zen 4 architecture- power, performance, expandability, and efficiency are at your fingertips. AMD Ryzenâ„˘ Threadripperâ„˘ processors enable artists, architects, and engineers to stay in their creative flow by addressing common lightly threaded and multithreaded bottlenecks.Â Accelerate workflows with next-gen professional GPUs and high-speed storage devices. AMD Ryzenâ„˘ Threadripperâ„˘ processors enable a variety of advanced workstation configurations.\nFEATURES:\n\nUp to 5.3 GHz\n32 Cores / 64 Threads\nsTR5 Socket\n\nAMD EXPOâ„˘ Technology\n\nAMD Ryzenâ„˘ Technologies\n\nSPECIFICATIONS:\n\nCPU Cores: 32\nThreads: 64\nBase Clock: 4.0 GHz\nMax Boost Clock: Up to 5.3 GHz\nTotal L1 Cache: 2MB\nTotal L2 Cache: 32MB\nTotal L3 Cache: 128MB\nUnlocked: Yes\nCMOS: TSMC 5nm FinFET\nCPU Socket: sTR5\nPCI ExpressÂ® Version: PCIe 5.0\nDefault TDP: 350W\nOS Support\n\nWindows 11 â€“ 64-Bit Edition\nRHEL x86 64-Bit\nUbuntu x86 64-Bit\n*Operating System (OS) support will vary by manufacturer.\n\n\nSupported Technologies\n\nAMD EXPOâ„˘ Technology\nAMD Ryzenâ„˘ Technologies\n\n\nThermal Solution: Not included\n\nWHATâ€™S IN THE BOX:\n\nAMD Ryzen Threadripper 7970WX 32 Core 5.3GHz CPU x1\n\n',52527.15,'https://www.syntech.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/100-100001351WOF_wr_01a.jpg','Components, CPU, AMD CPU',0,0,1,'2025-12-11 05:06:47.871','2025-12-11 05:06:47.871','New',0,NULL,NULL),('04e7