g a cutting-edge creative studio or a powerful local AI development environment, the Ryzen Threadripper 9970WX delivers unmatched performance, advanced virtualization support, and an exceptional computing experience. With support for the latest operating systems including Windows 11, Windows 10, Ubuntu, and RHEL, and designed for maximum scalability, this processor is your ultimate tool for accelerating creativity, innovation, and productivity.\nFEATURES:\n\nUp to 5.4GHz\n32 Cores / 64 Threads\nsTR5 Socket\n\nAMD EXPOâ„˘ Technology\n\nAMD Ryzenâ„˘ Technologies\nDesigned for enthusiast-level workstations and high-end desktops\nIdeal for artists, creators, architects, AI developers, and engineers\n\nSPECIFICATIONS:\n\nCPU Cores: 32\nThreads: 64\nBase Clock: 4.0GHz\nMax Boost Clock: Up to 5.4GHz\nTotal L1 Cache: 2560 KB\nTotal L2 Cache: 32MB\nTotal L3 Cache: 128MB\nUnlocked: Yes\nCMOS: TSMC 4nm FinFET\nCPU Socket: sTR5\nSupported Chipsets: TRX50\nPCI ExpressÂ® Version: PCIe 5.0\nDefault TDP: 350W\nOS Support\n\nWindows 11 â€“ 64-Bit Edition\nWindows 10 â€“ 64-Bit Edition\nRHEL x86 64-Bit\nUbuntu x86 64-Bit\n*Operating System (OS) support will vary by manufacturer.\n\n\nSupported Technologies\n\nAMD EXPOâ„˘ Technology\nAMD Ryzenâ„˘ Technologies\n\n\nThermal Solution: Not included\nSecurity, Virtualization, and Manageability\n\nDASH support: Yes\nAMD Memory Guard: Yes\nAMD Secure Processor Support: Yes\nWindows Secure Boot Support: Yes\nUEFI Secure Boot Support: Yes\nWindows Device Guard Support: Yes\nGuest Mode Execution (GMET) Trap Support: Yes\nVirtualization-Based Security (VBS) Support: Yes\nWindows Secured-Core PC Support: Yes\nFirmware TPM: Yes\nAMD-V (SVM) Support: Yes\nAMD-V Nested Paging (RVI) Support: Yes\nAMD AVIC (Interrupt Virtualization) Support: Yes\nAMD-Vi (I/O MMU Virtualization) Support: Yes\nSecond Level Address Translation (SLAT) Supported: Yes\nAdvanced Encryption Standard New Instructions (AES-NI): Yes\nAMD Enhanced Virus Protection (NX bit): Yes\n\n\n\nWHATâ€™S IN THE BOX:\n\nAMD Ryzen Threadripper 9970WX 32-Core 4.0GHz CPU x1\n\nPlease note: A discreet graphics card is required to use this CPU as it does not come with dedicated graphics on board.\n',58636.56,'https://www.syntech.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/100-100001595WOF_AMD-Ryzen-Threadripper-9960X-sTR5-24-core-CPU_wr_01a.jpg','Components, CPU, AMD CPU',0,0,1,'2025-12-11 05:06:47.673','2025-12-11 05:06:47.673','New',0,NULL,NULL),('0d600acd-a1a5-4336-b179-0a5ddae24de6','BX80768285K','Intel Core Ultra 9 285K LGA1851 3.7Ghz 24-Core CPU','The IntelÂ® Coreâ„˘ Ultra 9 285K CPU is a robust processor tailored to power modern digital workloads, from AI-driven tasks to intense gaming sessions. Part of Intelâ€™s Core Ultra Series, this CPU is designed for creators and gamers seeking cutting-edge performance with AI integration. With a combination of performance cores (P-cores) and eight efficient cores (E-cores), the Core Ultra 9 285K handles multitasking seamlessly, offloading background tasks to the E-cores, which frees up the P-cores to drive demanding applications and maintain top-notch responsiveness. The processorâ€™s powerful IntelÂ® Smart Cache (36MB) and support for DDR5 memory (up to 6400MHz) make it a versatile choice for creators who rely on high data throughput for large files and smooth, efficient workflow.\nGamers and Esports professionals will benefit from the Core Ultra 9 285Kâ€™s performance-focused architecture, which provides a Max Turbo Frequency of up to 5.70GHz for intense gaming moments. With 24 PCIe lanes and Thunderboltâ„˘ 5 support, this CPU is optimized for maximum expandability and high-speed connectivity. Built-in IntelÂ® Killerâ„˘ Networking reduces lag and packet loss, offering a more seamless online gaming experience, while AI features like IntelÂ® Gaussian & Neural Accelerator (GNA) help ensure clear communication by filtering background noise in voice comms. The processorâ€™s graphics capabilities also support high-resolution displays, including up to 8K resolution on DisplayPort and HDMI, making it a powerful engine for immersive gaming experiences.\nFor content creators, the IntelÂ® Coreâ„˘ Ultra 9 285Kâ€™s intelligent performance shines in AI-driven applications like generative AI and video production. IntelÂ® Deep Learning Boost enhances AI workloads directly on the CPU, speeding up AI model processing for creators working with machine learning or neural networks. The integrated IntelÂ® Connectivity Performance Suite optimizes network performance for smoother streaming, and Quick Sync Video accelerates video encoding, making this processor ideal for creators, streamers, and freelancers aiming to elevate their productivity. Together, these features make the Core Ultra 9 285K a powerhouse for users who need reliable, top-tier performance in both creative and gaming environments.\nFEATURES:\n\n24 Cores\n24 Threads\nMax Turbo Frequency of up to 5.70GHz\n36MB IntelÂ® Smart Cache\nSupport for DDR5 memory\nBuilt for serious gaming\nThe best overclocking experience\n\nSPECIFICATIONS:\n\nEssentials:\n\nProduct Collection: IntelÂ® Coreâ„˘ Ultra Processors (Series 2)\nCode Name: Products formerly Arrow Lake\nVertical Segment: Desktop\nProcessor Number: 285K\n\n\nCPU Specifications:\n\nTotal Cores: 24\n# of Performance-cores: 8\n# of Efficient-cores: 16\nTotal Threads: 24\nMax Turbo Frequency: 5.70GHz\nIntelÂ® Thermal Velocity Boost Frequency: 5.70GHz\nIntelÂ® Turbo Boost Max Technology 3.0 Frequency: 5.60GHz\nPerformance-core Max Turbo Frequency: 5.50GHz\nEfficient-core Max Turbo Frequency: 4.60GHz\nPerformance-core Base Frequency: 3.70GHz\nEfficient-core Base Frequency: 3.20GHz\nCache: 36 MB IntelÂ® Smart Cache\nTotal L2 Cache: 40 MB\nProcessor Base Power: 125 W\nMaximum Turbo Power: 250 W\nIntelÂ® Deep Learning Boost (IntelÂ® DL Boost) on CPU: Yes\nAI Software Frameworks Supported by CPU: OpenVINOâ„˘, WindowsML, DirectML, ONNX RT, WebNN\n\n\nMemory Specifications:\n\nMax Memory Size (depende