formance with optimised memory overclocking. Whether you\'re rendering 3D models, streaming, or dominating the latest AAA games, this processor delivers top-tier efficiency and processing power, making it the ideal choice for enthusiasts and professionals alike.\nFEATURES:\n\nUp to 5.5GHz\n12 Cores / 24 Threads\nAM5 Socket\nAMD EXPOâ„˘ Technology\nAMD Ryzenâ„˘ Technologies\n2nd gen AMD 3D V-Cacheâ„˘ Technology\n\nSPECIFICATIONS:\n\nCPU Cores: 12\nThreads: 24\nBase Clock: 4.4GHz\nMax Boost Clock: Up to 5.5GHz\nTotal L2 Cache: 12MB\nTotal L3 Cache: 128MB\nUnlocked: Yes\nCMOS: TSMC 4nm FinFET\nPackage: AM5\nPCI ExpressÂ® Version: PCIe 5.0\nDefault TDP / TDP: 120W\n\nWHAT\'S IN THE BOX:\n\nAMD Ryzen 9 9900X3D 12-Core 4.4GHz AM5 CPU â€“ Grey x1\n\n',12191.76,'https://www.syntech.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/AMD_100-100001368WOF_wr_01a.jpg','Components, CPU, AMD CPU',0,5,1,'2025-12-11 05:06:47.729','2025-12-11 05:06:47.729','New',0,NULL,NULL),('2c32f9c0-ef59-49f8-93ac-7bf18de68f9d','100-100001585BOX','AMD RYZEN 5 5600XT 6-Core 3.7GHZ AM4 CPU','Quick Specs\n\nSix cores and twelve threads deliver exceptional multitasking and gaming performance.\nBlazing-fast 4.7GHz boost clock for incredibly responsive gaming and application loading.\n32MB of L3 cache reduces latency, accelerating game load times and responsiveness.\nPCIe 4.0 support unlocks the potential of the latest graphics cards and NVMe SSDs.\nWraith Stealth cooler provides efficient and quiet cooling for optimal performance.\n\nDominate Gaming and Creation Tasks with the AMD Ryzen\nThe AMD Ryzen 5 5600XT CPUÂ  is engineered for gamers and content creators in South Africa who demand exceptional performance and reliability. This AMD Ryzen 5 CPU offers a perfect balance of power and efficiency, making it ideal for a wide range of tasks from playing the latest AAA titles to creating compelling content. Unlock the potential of your gaming rig with the AMD Ryzen 5 5600XT. Experience the responsiveness and power you need to conquer any challenge.\nExperience Unmatched Responsiveness\nFeaturing a boost clock of up to 4.7GHz, the AMD Ryzen 5 5600XT CPU delivers incredibly responsive performance in both gaming and demanding applications. Say goodbye to lag and hello to smoother gameplay, faster load times, and seamless multitasking. Powered by AMD\'s advanced processor technology, this AMD Ryzen 5 5600XT ensures a consistently superior computing experience.\nUnlock the Potential of PCIe 4.0\nTake full advantage of the latest PCIe 4.0 technology for lightning-fast data transfer rates and improved performance with compatible graphics cards and NVMe SSDs. The AMD Ryzen 5 CPU 5600XT allows you to fully utilise the capabilities of cutting-edge components, providing a superior, next-generation computing experience. Upgrade today and feel the difference.\nEfficient Cooling for Sustained Performance\nThe included Wraith Stealth cooler keeps your AMD Ryzen 5 CPU running cool and quiet, even during intense gaming sessions or demanding workloads. Enjoy stable and reliable performance without the distracting noise, thanks to AMD\'s efficient thermal solution. Focus on your game, not your system\'s temperature.\nOptimised for Modern Gaming and Applications\nThe AMD Ryzen 5 5600XT excels in both gaming and productivity tasks, ensuring smooth frame rates and fast rendering times. When paired with a compatible motherboard and RAM, this AMD Ryzen 5 CPU becomes the heart of a true powerhouse system. Experience the ultimate in performance and reliability.\nFEATURES:\n\nExperience fluid gaming and content creation with six cores and twelve threads in this AMD Ryzen 5 CPU.\nMaximise responsiveness with a 4.7GHz boost clock for snappy performance in demanding applications.\nAccelerate game load times and in-game responsiveness with 32MB of L3 cache.\nHarness the latest graphics cards and NVMe SSDs using PCIe 4.0 support.\nMaintain a cool and quiet system with the included Wraith Stealth cooler.\nEnjoy stable and reliable performance with a 65W TDP, balancing power and efficiency.\nBuild a high-performance system using a compatible AM4 motherboard.\nAchieve fast memory speeds and improved system responsiveness with support for DDR4 memory.\n\nSPECIFICATIONS:\n\nNumber of CPU Cores: 6\nNumber of Threads: 12\nBase Clock: 3.7GHz\nMaximum Boost Clock: Up to 4.7GHz\nTotal L2 Cache: 3MB\nTotal L3 Cache: 32MB\nUnlocked: Yes\nCMOS TSMC: 7nm FinFET\nPackage: AM4\nPCI Express Version: PCIe 4.0\nThermal Solution (PIB): Wraith Stealth\nDefault TDP / TDP: 65W\nSystem Memory Specification: Up to 3200MHz\nSystem Memory Type: DDR4\nSupported Technologies:\n\nAMD StoreMI Technology\nAMD Ryzen Master Utility\nAMD Ryzen VR-Ready Premium\n\n\n\nWHAT\'S IN THE BOX:\n\nAMD RYZEN 5 5600XT 6-Core 3.7GHZ AM4 CPU x1\nWraith Stealth CPU Cooler x1\n\nWhy AMD?\nAMD Ryzen processors have consistently delivered class-leading performance and reliability for gamers and content creators in South Africa. The AMD Ryzen 5 5600XT continues this tradition, providing exceptional value and cutting-edge features for a smooth and responsive computing experience. Trust AMD to power your next-generation gaming and content creation rig. Upgrade to an AMD Ryzen 5 CPU today and experience the difference.\nPlease note: A dedicated graphics card is required to use this CPU as it does not come with onboard graphics.\n',3375.12,'https://www.syntech.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/100-100001585BOX_AMD-RYZEN-5-5600XT-6-Core-3.7GHZ-AM4-CPU_wr_01a.jpg','Components, CPU, AMD CPU',0,31,1,'2025-12-11 05:06:47.723','2025-12-11 05:06:47.723','New',0,NULL,NULL),('2d63e489-3bd5-4636-b0b4-c6c331b9c529','BX8071512700','Intel 12th Gen Core i7-12700 LGA1700 2.1GHz 12-Core CPU','Take the next evolutionary leap with the performance hybrid architecture of 12th Generation IntelÂ® Coreâ„˘ processors. Get the performance you need, where you need it, whether youâ€™re a gamer, creator, streamer, or everyday user. Whatever youâ€™re into, do more of it, whenever you want with IntelÂ® 12 Generation processors. With unprecedented new performance hybrid architecture, 12th Gen IntelÂ® Coreâ„˘ processors offer a unique combination of Performance and Efficient-cores (P-core and E-core). That means real-world performance, intuitively scaled to match whatever youâ€™re doing.\nThe Performance-core is Intelâ€™s highest-performing CPU core ever. And itâ€™s designed to maximize single-thread performance and responsiveness for compute-intensive workloads like gaming and 3D design. The Efficient-core delivers multithreaded performance for tasks that can run in parallel (like image rendering), along with efficient offload of background tasks for modern multitasking.\nSo that Performance-cores and Efficient-cores can work seamlessly with the operating system, Intel built IntelÂ® Thread Director right into the hardware. Automatically monitoring and analyzing on-the-fly, IntelÂ® Thread Director guides the operating system, helping it place the right thread on the right core, at the right time. And it does it all dynamically, adapting scheduling guidance based on actual computing needs, not on static rules.\n12th Gen IntelÂ® Coreâ„˘ processors also support the next wave of discrete graphics cards and storage devices. These devices take advantage of increased throughput coming with PCIe 5.0 as well the higher speeds and bandwidth of DDR5 memory. With 12th Gen IntelÂ® Coreâ„˘ processors, standard, built-in features enable capabilities like noise suppression, auto-framing, and optimization for bandwidth and video resolution while gaming. That saves you time and lets you multitask in ways youâ€™ve only ever dreamed of, until now. From epic gaming to browsing to streaming to creating your next masterpiece, 12th Gen IntelÂ® Coreâ„˘ processors make it all entirely doable.\nFEATURES:\n\n12 Cores\n20 Threads\nMax Turbo Frequency of up to 4.90GHz\n25MB IntelÂ® Smart Cache\nSupport for DDR4 and DDR5 memory\nBuilt for serious gaming\nSmart solutions for enthusiasts and creators\nNearly 3x faster connectivity\n\nSPECIFICATIONS:\n\nEssentials:\n\nProduct Collection: 12th Generation IntelÂ® Coreâ„˘ i7 Processors\nCode Name: Products formerly Alder Lake\nVertical Segment: Desktop\nProcessor Number: i7-12700\nSocket Supported: FCLGA1700\n\n\nCPU Specifications:\n\nTotal Cores: 12\n# of Performance-cores: 8\n# of Efficient-cores: 4\nTotal Threads: 20\nMax Turbo Frequency: 4.90 GHz\nIntelÂ® Turbo Boost Max Technology 3.0 Frequency: 4.90 GHz\nPerformance-core Max Turbo Frequency: 4.80 GHz\nEfficient-core Max Turbo Frequency: 3.60 GHz\nPerformance-core Base Frequency: 2.10 GHz\nEfficient-core Base Frequency: 1.60 GHz\nCache: 25 MB IntelÂ® Smart Cache\nTotal L2 Cache: 12 MB\nProcessor Base Power: 65 W\nMaximum Turbo Power: 180 W\n\n\nMemory Specifications:\n\nMax Memory Size (dependent on memory type): 128 GB\nMemory Types:\n\nUp to DDR5 4800 MT/s\nUp to DDR4 3200 MT/s\n\n\nMax # of Memory Channels: 2\nMax Memory Bandwidth: 76.8 GB/s\n\n\nProcessor Graphics:\n\nProcessor Graphics: IntelÂ® UHD Graphics 770\nGraphics Base Frequency: 300 MHz\nGraphics Max Dynamic Frequency: 1.50 GHz\nGraphics Output: eDP 1.4b, DP 1.4a, HDMI 2.1\nExecution Units: 32\nMax Resolution (HDMI): 4096 x 2160 @ 60Hz\nMax Resolution (DP): 7680 x 4320 @ 60Hz\nMax Resolution (eDP - Integrated Flat Panel): 5120 x 3200 @ 120Hz\nDirectX* Support: 12\nOpenGL* Support: 4.5\nMulti-Format Codec Engines: 2\nIntelÂ® Quick Sync Video: Yes\nIntelÂ® Clear Video HD Technology: Yes\n# of Displays Supported: 4\nDevice ID: 0x4680\nOpenCL Support: 2.1\n\n\nExpansion Options:\n\nDirect Media Interface (DMI) Revision: 4.0\nMax # of DMI Lanes: 8\nScalability: 1S Only\nPCI Express Revision: 5.0 and 4.0\nPCI Express Configurations: Up to 1Ă—16+4, 2Ă—8+4\nMax # of PCI Express Lanes: 20\n\n\nAdvanced Features:\n\nIntelÂ® Gaussian & Neural Accelerator: 3.0\nIntelÂ® Thread Director: Yes\nIntelÂ® Deep Learning Boost (IntelÂ® DL Boost): Yes\nIntelÂ® Optaneâ„˘ Me