4:38.918','2025-12-07 21:54:38.918','New',0,NULL,NULL),('38431df1-60f5-43a3-b487-542398d71bc1','BX80768225','IntelÂ® Coreâ„˘ Ultra 5 225 LGA1851 3.30GHz 10-Core CPU','Quick Specs\n\nFeatures 10 Cores (6 Performance, 4 Efficient) for multitasking and efficiency.\nBoosts performance with a Max Turbo Frequency of 4.90GHz.\nSupports up to 256GB DDR5 memory for responsive performance.\nIntegrates Intel Graphics for crisp visuals and smooth media playback.\nAccelerates AI tasks with Intel AI Boost NPU for faster processing.\n\nUnleash the Power of 10 Cores with an Intel Desktop CPU\nThe Intel Core Ultra 5 225 processor delivers a revolutionary computing experience with its innovative hybrid architecture. Featuring 6 Performance-cores and 4 Efficient-cores, this CPU dynamically adjusts to your workload, providing exceptional performance and power efficiency. This makes it ideal for gamers, content creators, and professionals in South Africa who demand seamless multitasking and responsiveness from their Intel Desktop CPU.\nExperience Blazing-Fast Speeds with your Intel CPU for Gaming\nWith a Max Turbo Frequency of 4.90GHz, the Core Ultra 5 225 handles demanding applications and games with ease. The Performance-cores ensure lightning-fast response times, while the Efficient-cores optimise power consumption for extended battery life on mobile platforms. Whether you are rendering complex 3D models, editing high-resolution videos, or playing the latest AAA titles, this Intel CPU for gaming delivers unparalleled speed and fluidity.\nIntegrated Intel Graphics for Stunning Visuals\nThe integrated Intel Graphics provides vibrant visuals and smooth media playback. Enjoy your favourite movies, TV shows, and games in stunning detail, with support for resolutions up to 7680 x 4320 @ 60Hz via DisplayPort. The GPU also features advanced capabilities such as H.264 and H.265 encode/decode, AV1 encode/decode, and VP9 bitstream & decoding, ensuring compatibility with the latest video formats.\nAccelerate AI Tasks with Intel AI Boost NPU\nThe Intel AI Boost NPU (Neural Processing Unit) revolutionises AI workloads by providing dedicated hardware acceleration. With a peak throughput of 13 TOPS (Int8), the NPU significantly speeds up AI tasks such as image recognition, natural language processing, and machine learning. This allows you to leverage AI-powered applications and tools with exceptional performance and efficiency.\nFuture-Proof Your System with Advanced Features\nThe Intel Core Ultra 5 225 is equipped with a range of advanced features designed to future-proof your system. Support for up to 256GB of DDR5 memory ensures ample capacity for demanding applications, while PCI Express 5.0 and 4.0 support enables blazing-fast data transfer rates. Additionally, technologies such as Intel Thread Director, Intel Turbo Boost Technology 2.0, and Intel Virtualization Technology (VT-x) enhance performance, efficiency, and security.\nFEATURES:\n\nMaximise multitasking with 10 cores (6 Performance-cores, 4 Efficient-cores), optimising workload distribution.\nExperience faster response times with a Max Turbo Frequency of 4.90GHz, enhancing application performance.\nEnjoy seamless visuals with integrated Intel Graphics, supporting high-resolution displays and advanced video codecs.\nAccelerate AI-powered tasks with Intel AI Boost NPU, enabling faster machine learning and AI applications.\nSupport up to 256 GB of DDR5 memory for efficient data handling and seamless multitasking capabilities.\nConnect multiple high-speed devices using PCI Express 5.0 and 4.0 for increased bandwidth and performance.\nOptimise power consumption with Intel Thread Director, dynamically adjusting performance based on workload.\nEnhance data security with Intel Trusted Execution Technology, protecting sensitive data and applications.\nFacilitate smooth multitasking with Intel Hyper-Threading Technology, improving overall system responsiveness.\n\nSPECIFICATIONS:\n\nEssentials:\n\nProduct C